review_title: Overall its a nice table, very easy to put together
reviews: Overall its a nice table, very easy to put together. The only thing is that it scratches very easily. There was a nick from the packaging, and glue or something stuck to the table so it had to be wiped, but it cleaned up nicely.
Exactly as described. Well packaged delivery.
